DarkMouse::

Gets the transmission and frowns. "Get, and I got all worked up for 
nothing."
Transformed into mouse mode and started to hed over to the area in 
which KitKat had ordered them to go. She looked over at 
Quickstrike. "Well, let's get a move on it. I don't like sitting here 
in the open."


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, wilddance_mare@h... wrote:
> Quickstrike:
> 
> 
> 
> "What?" Quickstrike turned his head to Drill Bit. "Ah jus' got 
here, 
> an' we're leavin'? What uh waste of mah time!" He extended his arm 
> out into the battlefield and fired three times, not counting on 
> hitting any targets. He just needed to let of a little steam.
